---
import { profile } from "../../data/profile";
---

<section id="about" class="about container">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-tag">About Me</span>

    <h2>Building a Career in IT</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <p>
        I'm a Master of Applied Information Technology graduate based in
        Sydney, Australia, with a strong interest in cloud technologies,
        networking, systems administration and cybersecurity.
      </p>

      <p>
        I enjoy solving technical problems, building home lab environments,
        learning new technologies and improving my practical IT skills through
        projects and continuous learning.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm currently seeking an entry-level IT opportunity where I can
        contribute, learn from experienced professionals and continue growing
        my technical expertise.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <h3>Currently Focused On</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>☁ Azure Administration</li>
        <li>🖥 Windows Server</li>
        <li>🔐 Active Directory</li>
        <li>🌐 Networking</li>
        <li>🛡 Cybersecurity</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>